      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_004",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我选择地铁，下楼进站，看着前方长长的队伍。",
      "sentence_index": 4,
      "char_start": 95,
      "char_end": 124,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_005",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我排进队伍，打卡进站，看着时钟，额头冒汗。",
      "sentence_index": 5,
      "char_start": 125,
      "char_end": 152,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_006",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "时间将近，队伍仍长，我攥紧拳头，前方有领导，不能迟到！",
      "sentence_index": 6,
      "char_start": 153,
      "char_end": 191,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_007",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "打印文件、整理资料、处理报表，这些事在等着我，看着队伍，再看时钟，我面露惊讶，额头冒汗。",
      "sentence_index": 7,
      "char_start": 192,
      "char_end": 248,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_008",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "队伍缓慢前移，时钟转动，队伍仍长，时钟再走，我满头大汗，雨势渐大。",
      "sentence_index": 8,
      "char_start": 250,
      "char_end": 295,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_009",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "终于轮到我，打卡进站，顺利通过，我露出微笑，快步冲向扶梯，再快步前行。",
      "sentence_index": 9,
      "char_start": 296,
      "char_end": 344,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_010",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "到了地铁口，红灯亮起，车门开启！",
      "sentence_index": 10,
      "char_start": 345,
      "char_end": 365,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_011",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我冲上车门，车门开启，我挤入车厢，地铁关门启动。",
      "sentence_index": 11,
      "char_start": 366,
      "char_end": 400,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_012",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我看着雨，面露轻松，站在车厢里，看着车门上的警示标识。",
      "sentence_index": 12,
      "char_start": 401,
      "char_end": 440,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_013",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "有人递给我物品。",
      "sentence_index": 13,
      "char_start": 441,
      "char_end": 450,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_014",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "地铁线路图上，我从起点到换乘站，再到终点。",
      "sentence_index": 14,
      "char_start": 451,
      "char_end": 481,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_015",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "背着包的人从我身边挤过，一个又一个，我被夹在中间，表情从生气变为难过，愈发沮丧。",
      "sentence_index": 15,
      "char_start": 482,
      "char_end": 540,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_016",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "看着线路图，离换乘站越来越近，我盯着座位，快步冲过去抢座。",
      "sentence_index": 16,
      "char_start": 541,
      "char_end": 585,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_017",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "终于跑到座位前，坐下了。",
      "sentence_index": 17,
      "char_start": 586,
      "char_end": 604,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_018",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "地铁从起点开往换乘站，再往终点驶去。",
      "sentence_index": 18,
      "char_start": 606,
      "char_end": 632,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_019",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "有人挥手，我闻到异味！",
      "sentence_index": 19,
      "char_start": 633,
      "char_end": 648,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_020",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "有人在旁说话，声音清晰，气味冲来，我恨不得戴上口罩！",
      "sentence_index": 20,
      "char_start": 649,
      "char_end": 686,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_021",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "地铁禁止饮食标识清晰，车厢内无人进食。",
      "sentence_index": 21,
      "char_start": 687,
      "char_end": 713,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_022",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我仍面露怒色，有人穿高跟鞋踩了我，我露出震惊的表情！",
      "sentence_index": 22,
      "char_start": 714,
      "char_end": 752,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_023",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "地铁到站，红灯亮起，车门开启，我跟着队伍下车。",
      "sentence_index": 23,
      "char_start": 753,
      "char_end": 786,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_024",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我又想起座位，跑过去抢，坐下后露出微笑。",
      "sentence_index": 24,
      "char_start": 787,
      "char_end": 814,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_025",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "地铁到了下一站，快到终点，我看着空座与有人的座位，一位孕妇站在旁边，我看了看座位，起身让座。",
      "sentence_index": 25,
      "char_start": 815,
      "char_end": 882,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_026",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "地铁到站，停稳。",
      "sentence_index": 26,
      "char_start": 883,
      "char_end": 893,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_027",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我跟着人流下车，跑上扶梯，快步冲向写字楼。",
      "sentence_index": 27,
      "char_start": 894,
      "char_end": 920,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_028",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我快步跑进电梯，按下上下键。",
      "sentence_index": 28,
      "char_start": 922,
      "char_end": 941,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_029",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "看了看时钟，又按了一次，电梯终于抵达。",
      "sentence_index": 29,
      "char_start": 942,
      "char_end": 967,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_030",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我跟着队伍进电梯，按下89楼，电梯门关上，开始上行。",
      "sentence_index": 30,
      "char_start": 968,
      "char_end": 1002,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_031",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "到了2楼，电梯停下，我面露怒色，想走楼梯，但2楼楼梯口被堵住，只能继续上行至3楼。",
      "sentence_index": 31,
      "char_start": 1003,
      "char_end": 1058,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_032",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "到了4楼，电梯又停，我面露惊讶；到了5楼再停，我面露难过，汗水直流。",
      "sentence_index": 32,
      "char_start": 1059,
      "char_end": 1110,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_033",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "电梯一路停靠，我从生气变为愤怒，最终濒临崩溃。",
      "sentence_index": 33,
      "char_start": 1111,
      "char_end": 1146,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_034",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "到了87楼，电梯再次停下，我面露怒色，有人走进电梯，电梯反复开关，上上下下！",
      "sentence_index": 34,
      "char_start": 1147,
      "char_end": 1201,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_035",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我按下关门键，再按！",
      "sentence_index": 35,
      "char_start": 1202,
      "char_end": 1215,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_036",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "广播响起：\"电梯限乘10人！超过10人禁止运行！\"",
      "sentence_index": 36,
      "char_start": 1216,
      "char_end": 1246,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_037",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我看着电梯，面露烦躁。",
      "sentence_index": 37,
      "char_start": 1247,
      "char_end": 1261,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_038",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "看着挤在电梯里的人群，人数堪比木乃伊方阵，我面露怒色。",
      "sentence_index": 38,
      "char_start": 1262,
      "char_end": 1299,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_039",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "有人指着电梯门，示意里面的人不要出去，我彻底愤怒了！",
      "sentence_index": 39,
      "char_start": 1300,
      "char_end": 1339,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_040",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "时间到了！",
      "sentence_index": 40,
      "char_start": 1340,
      "char_end": 1345,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_041",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我走进电梯，开门，快步前行，直行，下楼，再直行，上楼，折返，又下楼，再直行。",
      "sentence_index": 41,
      "char_start": 1346,
      "char_end": 1399,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_042",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "到了88楼，我继续前行，上楼，折返，下楼，再走，到了89楼！",
      "sentence_index": 42,
      "char_start": 1400,
      "char_end": 1440,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_043",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我快步跑进电梯。",
      "sentence_index": 43,
      "char_start": 1441,
      "char_end": 1450,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_044",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我下楼、直行、再直行，转弯，突然弯腰咳嗽，缓过来后继续直行、转弯、再直行。",
      "sentence_index": 44,
      "char_start": 1451,
      "char_end": 1508,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_045",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我刷工牌、用手机开门，一路快步走，一边挥手打招呼，再挥手，和一位女士道别。",
      "sentence_index": 45,
      "char_start": 1509,
      "char_end": 1565,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_046",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我转弯、直行、开门、走到办公桌前坐下。",
      "sentence_index": 46,
      "char_start": 1566,
      "char_end": 1594,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_047",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "看着时钟，我额头冒汗。",
      "sentence_index": 47,
      "char_start": 1595,
      "char_end": 1610,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_048",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "做出胜利的手势！",
      "sentence_index": 48,
      "char_start": 1611,
      "char_end": 1621,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_049",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "凌晨两点，我躺在床上，很快就进入了梦乡。",
      "sentence_index": 49,
      "char_start": 1623,
      "char_end": 1651,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_050",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "在梦里，我看到两个人在激烈地争吵。",
      "sentence_index": 50,
      "char_start": 1652,
      "char_end": 1676,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_051",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "接着，我梦见了 2012 年世界末日的场景，巨大的海浪淹没了地球，人们纷纷逃到山上避难。",
      "sentence_index": 51,
      "char_start": 1677,
      "char_end": 1738,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_052",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "凌晨五点，我开始做梦。",
      "sentence_index": 52,
      "char_start": 1739,
      "char_end": 1753,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_053",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "在梦里，我走了很长的路，看到了闪电，然后走进了一栋房子。",
      "sentence_index": 53,
      "char_start": 1754,
      "char_end": 1794,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_054",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我在房子里转来转去，感觉一直在循环往复。",
      "sentence_index": 54,
      "char_start": 1795,
      "char_end": 1825,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_055",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "接着，我坐上了飞机，飞到了天上，看到了云朵和热气球。",
      "sentence_index": 55,
      "char_start": 1826,
      "char_end": 1864,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_056",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我坐热气球飞向太阳，然后又开始做梦。",
      "sentence_index": 56,
      "char_start": 1865,
      "char_end": 1889,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_057",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "在梦里，我看到了太阳、房子、城堡、汽车和美丽的花朵。",
      "sentence_index": 57,
      "char_start": 1890,
      "char_end": 1924,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_058",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我和很多人一起看花，然后继续做梦。",
      "sentence_index": 58,
      "char_start": 1925,
      "char_end": 1948,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_059",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我变成了超人，拥有钻石和皇冠，还有机器人。",
      "sentence_index": 59,
      "char_start": 1949,
      "char_end": 1978,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_060",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我坐上火箭，遇到了下雨，然后从大楼上掉下来，感到非常惊讶。",
      "sentence_index": 60,
      "char_start": 1979,
      "char_end": 2021,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_061",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我在梦里看到两个人在激烈地争吵，然后惊讶地醒来。",
      "sentence_index": 61,
      "char_start": 2022,
      "char_end": 2055,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_062",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我看到电视和卫生间，电视里的人在不停地移动。",
      "sentence_index": 62,
      "char_start": 2056,
      "char_end": 2086,
      "children": []
    },
    {
      "unit_id": "sent_063",
      "unit_type": "sentence",
      "text": "我看着电视，感到有些迷茫。",
      "sentence_index": 63,
      "char_start": 2087,
      "char_end": 2103,
      "children": []
    }
  ],
  "annotations": [
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_001",
      "target_id": "sent_001",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我穿过人行横道，一边看着手机地图上的定位，一边从西往东走。",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "保留方向和动作，补充“手机地图”使“城市定位”更自然。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_002",
      "target_id": "sent_002",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我在乘坐公交车和地铁之间拿不定主意。",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "用“拿不定主意”替换“犹豫”，更口语化。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_003",
      "target_id": "sent_003",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我瞄了一眼手机上的信号强度，路过一块写着限速280的路牌，前面有施工或危险的警示标志，路上堵得非常厉害，公交车根本开不过去。",
      "confidence": 0.92,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "补充“施工或危险”使“警示标识”更具体。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_004",
      "target_id": "sent_004",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "于是我决定坐地铁，走下楼梯进到站里，看到前面排着好长好长的队伍。",
      "confidence": 0.96,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "“下楼进站”明确为“走下楼梯进到站里”。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_005",
      "target_id": "sent_005",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我赶紧排进队伍，刷卡过了闸机，看了一眼时间，急得额头上都冒汗了。",
      "confidence": 0.94,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "“打卡进站”译为“刷卡过了闸机”更贴合地铁场景。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_006",
      "target_id": "sent_006",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "眼看着时间快来不及了，可队伍还是那么长，我急得握紧了拳头，心里想着前面还有领导等着呢，千万不能迟到啊！",
      "confidence": 0.93,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "补充心理活动，增强情感表达。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_007",
      "target_id": "sent_007",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "打印文件、整理资料、处理报表，这一堆活儿还在等着我呢。我看了看队伍，又看了看时间，惊讶得张大了嘴，脑门上全是汗。",
      "confidence": 0.94,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "“面露惊讶”具体化为“惊讶得张大了嘴”。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_008",
      "target_id": "sent_008",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "队伍慢慢往前挪，时间一分一秒地过去，队伍还是那么长。我急得满头大汗，偏偏这时候雨也越下越大了。",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "“时钟转动”意译为“时间一分一秒地过去”。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_009",
      "target_id": "sent_009",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "好不容易终于轮到我了，我赶紧刷卡进站，总算顺利通过了。我开心地笑了，飞快地跑向扶梯，又加快脚步往前走。",
      "confidence": 0.96,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "突出“终于轮到我了”的如释重负感。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_010",
      "target_id": "sent_010",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "赶到地铁口的时候，正好红灯闪烁，车门打开了！",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "简洁有力，保留感叹情绪。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_011",
      "target_id": "sent_011",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我猛地冲上车，门还开着，我拼命挤进车厢，随后地铁关上门启动了。",
      "confidence": 0.94,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "“冲上”“挤入”用“猛地冲上”“拼命挤进”强化动作感。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_012",
      "target_id": "sent_012",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我看着窗外的雨，终于松了口气，站在车厢里，望着车门上贴着的警示标志。",
      "confidence": 0.96,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "“面露轻松”译为“终于松了口气”。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_013",
      "target_id": "sent_013",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "有个陌生人递给我一个东西。",
      "confidence": 0.99,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "句子简单，直接重述。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_014",
      "target_id": "sent_014",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我盯着地铁线路图，心里盘算着从起点坐到换乘站，再换乘到终点。",
      "confidence": 0.93,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "补充“心里盘算着”使句子更有叙事感。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_015",
      "target_id": "sent_015",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "背着双肩包的人一个接一个地从我身边挤过去，我被卡在人群中间，脸上的表情从生气慢慢变成了难过，心里越来越沮丧。",
      "confidence": 0.92,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "长句拆解，使情绪变化更清晰。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_016",
      "target_id": "sent_016",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我看着线路图，发现离换乘站越来越近了，眼睛死死盯着空座位，快步冲过去抢座。",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "强化“抢座”的紧迫感。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_017",
      "target_id": "sent_017",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我终于跑到座位前面，一屁股坐了下来。",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "“一屁股坐下来”更口语化。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_018",
      "target_id": "sent_018",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "地铁从起点出发，开往换乘站，然后再往终点方向开去。",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "直接重述。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_019",
      "target_id": "sent_019",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "旁边有人挥了挥手，我突然闻到一股刺鼻的怪味！",
      "confidence": 0.96,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "“异味”改为“刺鼻的怪味”更形象。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_020",
      "target_id": "sent_020",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "有人在旁边说话，声音听得清清楚楚，那股气味直冲过来，我真恨不得赶紧戴上一个口罩！",
      "confidence": 0.94,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "保留夸张语气“恨不得”。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_021",
      "target_id": "sent_021",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "车厢里明明贴着禁止饮食的标识，清清楚楚的，也确实没有人吃东西。",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "强化对比逻辑。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_022",
      "target_id": "sent_022",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我还是满脸不高兴，结果有人穿着高跟鞋狠狠地踩了我一脚，我疼得瞪大了眼睛，一脸震惊！",
      "confidence": 0.93,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "补充“疼得”使因果关系更清楚。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_023",
      "target_id": "sent_023",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "地铁到站了，红灯亮起来，车门打开，我跟着人群下了车。",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "直接重述。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_024",
      "target_id": "sent_024",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我又想起了那个座位，赶紧跑过去抢，坐下之后心满意足地笑了。",
      "confidence": 0.96,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "“露出微笑”具体化为“心满意足地笑了”。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_025",
      "target_id": "sent_025",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "地铁开到下一站，快到终点的时候，我看到有空座也有人坐着，旁边站着一位孕妇。我看了看身边的座位，犹豫了一下，站起来把座位让给了她。",
      "confidence": 0.92,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "长句拆分，补充“犹豫了一下”使人物更真实。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_026",
      "target_id": "sent_026",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "地铁到站，停稳了。",
      "confidence": 0.99,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "直接重述。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_027",
      "target_id": "sent_027",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我随着人流下了车，跑上自动扶梯，快步冲向办公楼。",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "直接重述。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_028",
      "target_id": "sent_028",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我飞快地跑进电梯，胡乱按了上下键。",
      "confidence": 0.96,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "“按下上下键”用“胡乱按了”体现焦急。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_029",
      "target_id": "sent_029",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我又看了看手表，不耐烦地又按了一次，电梯总算来了。",
      "confidence": 0.94,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "补充“不耐烦地”体现情绪。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_030",
      "target_id": "sent_030",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我跟着人群进了电梯，按下了89楼的按钮，电梯门关上了，开始往上走。",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "直接重述。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_031",
      "target_id": "sent_031",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "到了2楼，电梯突然停了，我气得脸都绿了。本来想走楼梯，可是2楼的楼梯口被人堵得死死的，没办法，只好又回到电梯里，继续上到3楼。",
      "confidence": 0.91,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "拆分为更自然的短句，补充逻辑。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_032",
      "target_id": "sent_032",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "到了4楼，电梯又停下了，我惊讶得说不出话；到了5楼又停了一次，我难过极了，汗珠止不住地往下掉。",
      "confidence": 0.93,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "用具体描述替换抽象情绪词。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_033",
      "target_id": "sent_033",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "电梯几乎每层都停，我的心情从生气一步步升级为愤怒，最后彻底崩溃了。",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "“一路停靠”译为“几乎每层都停”。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_034",
      "target_id": "sent_034",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "到了87楼，电梯又停了下来，我气得满脸通红。有人挤了进来，电梯门反复开关，一会儿上一会儿下，简直没完没了！",
      "confidence": 0.94,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "保留感叹语气。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_035",
      "target_id": "sent_035",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我使劲按关门的按钮，按了一遍又一遍！",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "简洁有力。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_036",
      "target_id": "sent_036",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "这时广播响了：“电梯最多乘10个人！超过10个人就不能开！”",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "直接转述广播内容。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_037",
      "target_id": "sent_037",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我看着电梯里挤得满满当当的人，心里烦躁极了。",
      "confidence": 0.96,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "补充“挤得满满当当”使“面露烦躁”更有依据。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_038",
      "target_id": "sent_038",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我看着塞在电梯里的人群，那密度简直跟古埃及的木乃伊方阵有得一拼，我气得直瞪眼。",
      "confidence": 0.92,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "保留并解释“木乃伊方阵”这个比喻。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_039",
      "target_id": "sent_039",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "还有人指着电梯门，示意里面的人别出去，我这下彻底被激怒了！",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "强调愤怒的顶点。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_040",
      "target_id": "sent_040",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "上班时间快到了！",
      "confidence": 0.99,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "简洁，保留紧迫感。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_041",
      "target_id": "sent_041",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我冲进电梯（另一部），开门，快步往前走，直走，下楼，再直走，上楼，掉头，又下楼，接着直走。",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "保留动作序列，补充“另一部”使逻辑连贯。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_042",
      "target_id": "sent_042",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "到了88楼，我继续往前走，上楼，掉头，下楼，再走，终于到了89楼！",
      "confidence": 0.96,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "保留“终于”表达抵达的如释重负。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_043",
      "target_id": "sent_043",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我赶紧跑进了另一部电梯。",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "直接重述。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_044",
      "target_id": "sent_044",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我下楼、直走、继续直走，拐了个弯，突然弯腰咳嗽起来。喘过气之后，我继续直走、拐弯、再直走。",
      "confidence": 0.93,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "拆分长句，使动作更清晰。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_045",
      "target_id": "sent_045",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我刷工牌、用手机刷开门禁，一路小跑，一边挥手跟同事打招呼，又挥了挥手，和一位女士道别。",
      "confidence": 0.94,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "“手机开门”明确为“用手机刷开门禁”。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_046",
      "target_id": "sent_046",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我拐弯、直走、开门，走到自己的办公桌前面坐了下来。",
      "confidence": 0.96,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "直接重述。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_047",
      "target_id": "sent_047",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我看了一眼时钟，额头上又冒出了汗。",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "直接重述。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_048",
      "target_id": "sent_048",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我兴奋地比了个胜利的手势！",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "补充“兴奋地”表达情绪。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_049",
      "target_id": "sent_049",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "凌晨两点，我躺在床上，不一会儿就沉沉地睡着了。",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "“进入了梦乡”译为“沉沉地睡着了”。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_050",
      "target_id": "sent_050",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "梦里，我看见两个人正吵得不可开交。",
      "confidence": 0.96,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "“激烈地争吵”译为“吵得不可开交”。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_051",
      "target_id": "sent_051",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "接着，我梦到了2012年世界末日的样子，滔天的巨浪把整个地球都淹没了，人们拼命地逃到山上去避难。",
      "confidence": 0.94,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "“巨大的海浪”用“滔天的巨浪”更形象。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_052",
      "target_id": "sent_052",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "凌晨五点，我又开始做起梦来。",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "直接重述。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_053",
      "target_id": "sent_053",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "梦里，我走了很长很长的路，看到了闪电，然后走进了一栋房子里。",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "直接重述。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_054",
      "target_id": "sent_054",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我在房子里转来转去，感觉好像一直在原地打转，怎么也走不出去。",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "补充“怎么也走不出去”使“循环往复”更具体。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_055",
      "target_id": "sent_055",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "接着，我坐上了飞机，飞到了天上，看见了云朵和热气球。",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "直接重述。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_056",
      "target_id": "sent_056",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我又坐上热气球朝着太阳飞去，然后又开始做别的梦了。",
      "confidence": 0.96,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "直接重述。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_057",
      "target_id": "sent_057",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "在梦里，我看见了太阳、房子、城堡、汽车，还有漂亮的花朵。",
      "confidence": 0.98,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "直接重述。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_058",
      "target_id": "sent_058",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我和好多人一起赏花，然后继续做起了梦。",
      "confidence": 0.97,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "直接重述。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_059",
      "target_id": "sent_059",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我摇身一变成了超人，拥有了钻石、王冠，还有一个机器人。",
      "confidence": 0.96,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "“我变成了”用“摇身一变成了”更生动。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_060",
      "target_id": "sent_060",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我坐上火箭，途中遇到了下雨，然后从一栋大楼上摔了下去，吓得我心惊胆战。",
      "confidence": 0.93,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "补充“吓得我心惊胆战”强化惊讶感。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_061",
      "target_id": "sent_061",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "梦里我又看到两个人吵得不可开交，然后猛地惊醒过来，一脸吃惊。",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "“惊讶地醒来”用“猛地惊醒过来，一脸吃惊”。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_062",
      "target_id": "sent_062",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我看到电视开着，卫生间亮着灯，电视里的人一直在动来动去。",
      "confidence": 0.94,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "补充“开着”“亮着灯”使场景更清晰。"
    },
    {
      "annotation_id": "ann_sent_063",
      "target_id": "sent_063",
      "target_type": "sentence",
      "task_id": "free_translation",
      "task_label_zh": "自由翻译",
      "task_label_en": "Free Translation",
      "value": "我呆呆地看着电视，心里空落落的，不知道自己在想什么。",
      "confidence": 0.93,
      "llm_used": true,
      "llm_name": "DeepSeek",
      "annotator_note": "“感到有些迷茫”具体化为“心里空落落的，不知道自己在想什么”。"
    }
  ]
}